metadata.name: Gnostica Cetacea 1 - Delphinus Delphis
metadata.description:
”Gnosis” means direct knowledge of spiritual mysteries. 

This collection explores the direct knowledge 
about life in communion with nature which 
we can receive from our cetacean cohabitants on this earth.
